{"title":"Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Caidas Adulto Mayor NICE2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Caidas en el\\NAdulto Mayor","guid":"458DeZlXSXqumgod2K63gw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definicion y\\NConcepto","guid":"2GOBeD8JSi6-neJylZpCDA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Evento inadvertido con desplazamiento al suelo o nivel inferior","guid":"7J54OPKHTp-GZAPDBzpa4A","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"SIN perdida de conciencia previa NI perdida de tono postural","guid":"-Vpvx3y3R06XlitwKIY_Nw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"SINDROME GERIATRICO → no diagnostico aislado → sintoma de condicion de base","guid":"9WCZUFJnQty0lswPtEZfVQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"No es evento normal del envejecimiento → signo de fragilidad o patologia","guid":"ejQCyA43Qoec6phkLcNTTQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Sincope puede simular caida si hay amnesia retrograda","guid":"r5SVOiV1Svu7NvWFqyR99w","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiologia","guid":"8CJCthV1RliYbWMda4qSrw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Comunidad","guid":"8eWvKJtdQGaXq4scv2su-A","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"1/3 de >65a caen en 1 ano","guid":"9DorTKu3SP2rDSH9hV9X8g","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"40% de >80a caen al menos 1 vez/ano","guid":"-eau6g6wTButW9PLkSBxEQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"60% de los que caen 1 vez → vuelven a caer","guid":"Pm3mv3XlQT25jGz_qWZ9ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Institucionalizados","guid":"c9QpBxWZQFm0Sx5rIv58xA","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"50% caen anualmente (rango 30-56%)","guid":"09inIJcyQG26zwTANE5taQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"21% caen el PRIMER MES de ingreso → vigilancia extrema","guid":"X-9m-ymyRQKHTSkKPH8LuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"7","text":"Hospitalizados","guid":"ltNYrwFoQfChrCDbj2KqMw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"2% en sala general","guid":"RJy27Rl1S92Jj897rHMqYQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"27% en UGA","guid":"z-Fhi-3SQVmh3qvo3PfPkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"7","text":"Mayoria ocurren de dia → solo 20% entre 21:00-07:00","guid":"ps_rCeRwQ7mkyyngSyxxlA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"7","text":"Caidas <2m → mecanismo comun de trauma mayor en AM","guid":"6qtkzsDVSPW-Q7smWEU9lg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"7","text":"PRIMERA causa de fractura de cadera (95%)","guid":"V7-zhXJoTZWJ_Yq0Jzggig","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Mecanismo de Caida y Fracturas","guid":"9XHa6IOuRM20nB6Y2xYYBQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Anteroposterior → fractura de muneca (65-75a)","guid":"WQbBNMpsSsWOVUHIXtGJsg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Lateral → fractura de cadera (>75a)","guid":"it5wfSGrTaWwNIEWeFvf6A","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Perdida del reflejo de paracaidas → cambio patron muñeca a cadera","guid":"H2GQTJvlQCCa5vCiDcbhcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Posterior → poco relacionado con fracturas","guid":"EylCXuOvSoy413GnhN33Lg","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"21","text":"Sincopes → 2-10% de las causas de caidas","guid":"h-VFhxHQTdOQPtjt7NZ-vA","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Fisiologia de Marcha y Equilibrio","guid":"iWxLDG-QTqeCPAAVNtsvPQ","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Sistemas implicados","guid":"UcCrG4XzSISm4gM9UHiFIQ","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Aferente (sensorial) → visual + vestibular + propioceptivo","guid":"fSLvHDauQZSzjDUY_qBATg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"SNC → corteza frontal (planificacion) + ganglios basales (dopamina) + cerebelo + tronco + medula","guid":"6pYECrLsQNeSZQlJ08HRKw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Efector → CV, huesos, articulaciones, pies","guid":"c6uh8EXjQR2knojVtJpKTg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"Cognitivo → atencion y funcion ejecutiva influyen directamente","guid":"GJ8h_pBLS5ih9RjBqplCTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"27","text":"Estrategias posturales","guid":"reyO9s8GQy67KNx2_7iuVw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Estrategia de tobillo (perturbaciones pequenas)","guid":"16OXBcPKSKeNYovGiXSwaA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Estrategia de cadera (perturbaciones mayores)","guid":"pDp2mYgvTVaBq1jU-2uGqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"27","text":"Cambios con envejecimiento","guid":"UgCaxuSLT1eTFF_e_2LBOw","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Velocidad marcha estable hasta 70a → luego -15%/decada marcha comun, -20% marcha rapida","guid":"SFBsWChdT4mFwK6ztkuR_g","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Pasos mas cortos al mismo ritmo (debilidad pantorrilla)","guid":"BIb5lcd_SBKs0HSLvq1jhA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Tiempo doble apoyo → jovenes 18% vs AM >26%","guid":"bfwAzPtATtGfMUTQmupNrQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Cifosis dorsal desplaza centro gravedad anterior","guid":"E-zKzLlQS4C_hzhg29JurA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"Menor flexion plantar y extension rodilla","guid":"eVNjOEcjRtSbf-rEfkdL0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"27","text":"Marcha senil → CONTROVERSIA → alteraciones son marcadores precoces de patologia (demencia)","guid":"fj6AX6bPTU-vxyBfMSGuWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo","guid":"PpaNC2LARFiXlY_vXxLZzw","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Intrinsicos","guid":"FddbchyVT1iKivsISsdh7w","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"DEBILIDAD MUSCULAR → RR/OR 4.9 (1.9-10.3) → PRINCIPAL","guid":"hAa0dkZjS_aDJ88nG6V3PQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Deficit de balance → OR 3.2 (1.6-5.4)","guid":"AtLufeBQS5a_eBO3b6yD9w","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Deficit de marcha → OR 3.0 (1.7-4.8)","guid":"EWU6I4yiQB61_e4Ta2c3MA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Deficit visual → OR 2.8 (1.1-7.4)","guid":"K6OzERY9RmGruGNfHp5ArQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Contraste y profundidad > agudeza visual pura","guid":"VNd_AlUjS7-ecP_mtI7c1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"Limitacion movilidad → OR 2.5 (1.0-5.3)","guid":"iI35eNu2T-ORvdnPlBGCXg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"44","text":"Deterioro cognitivo → OR 2.4 (2.0-4.7)","guid":"f-tw7uhVQ5aebcU5m1ictg","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Riesgo +20% por cada punto menos en MMSE","guid":"xNHw1XWFTwK3f4lrS0HYWg","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"DCL NO amnesico (frontal/ejecutivo) → caen MAS que Alzheimer tipico","guid":"D8V7VWfGTGCe691L0J-TQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"44","text":"Estado funcional alterado → OR 2.0 (1.0-3.1)","guid":"Nd8nZriXSqe0sBc8cHV-8g","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"44","text":"Hipotension ortostatica → OR 1.9 (1.0-3.4)","guid":"Ph-AUkbGTySXKy3_ZKcHiQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"30% en >65a, 70% institucionalizados","guid":"U8metnuuRUaA-jN6qPwtvQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Hipotension postprandial → caida PAS >=20mmHg 2h post comida","guid":"ihILVh-iQ16AjeDtvA8LGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"44","text":"Edad → riesgo lesion seria 4x mayor en >85a vs 65-74a","guid":"obz6Lwm6QpGLkFgPgM6JEw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"44","text":"Sexo femenino → base marcha estrecha, osteoporosis, sarcopenia","guid":"t7k6QDgrT-WlZTTBceImbg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"44","text":"Caidas previas → predictor potente → 2da caida tiene mayor mortalidad","guid":"PadPYHmKSVuOT0ZAMNt3WQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"44","text":"Vitamina D <10 → mayor perdida masa muscular; <20 → peor performance","guid":"vvvNaV6OROWaaTGnIRstiQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"44","text":"Diabetes → neuropatia + vision + cognicion; insulina RR 2.76","guid":"SzFl4rhVQjSxAzzKGtCuhg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"44","text":"Parkinson → rigidez, bradicinesia","guid":"YSAkGdk4SAG56rezsGKAgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"43","text":"Extrinsecos (ambientales)","guid":"3krv3-0FSgeUmULa8itUaw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Calzado inadecuado → zapatillas, calcetines, descalzo, taco >2.5cm","guid":"Y4tk2v4RQs-sCAZKHK1sqA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Domicilio → bano, alfombras, iluminacion → bajar escaleras > subir","guid":"iiwYQMmYQUGSmIopemq4CQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Institucionalizacion → FR en si mismo","guid":"72bW_AKASnGZe2HkZDd2_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"43","text":"Precipitantes (estresores agudos)","guid":"YB03Eb12RYmySKUQEkJniA","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Resbalone, tropiezos","guid":"EOSkp2U3TEWhAgh0j1juPg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"Sincope, mareo agudo, convulsion","guid":"h26f5c-3RR-Xxeduo7Ma8A","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"Inicio o ajuste farmacologico → MAYOR riesgo primeras 24h","guid":"Ffitnw-oSZa72dw2y7yGNQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Farmacos y Caidas","guid":"_gwyZZxGS0el5kSa8KRQBw","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"PRINCIPAL factor de riesgo MODIFICABLE","guid":"GJsCb1ugRUSkv6TaBcRq4w","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Psicofármacos → aumentan riesgo hasta 40%","guid":"gd1DWXiRTj6xM41WwzF7Mg","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Antidepresivos → OR 1.68 (1.47-1.91); ATC > ISRS > Trazodona","guid":"x0XyY-lMSAuYZwt3TM3nXQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"Antipsicoticos → OR 1.59 (1.37-1.83)","guid":"Ii5EjyiwRh6rkPmCoFOs5Q","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"Hipnoticos/sedantes → OR 1.47 (1.35-1.62)","guid":"Vo_cJhgATbChO8klDRaQyA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"Benzodiazepinas → OR 1.57 (1.43-1.72)","guid":"1CqE1tL-SnWGI2RbfVdNew","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"Cardiovasculares","guid":"_POAmVrvTCiXKmBcHG0pHg","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Antihipertensivos → OR 1.24 (1.01-1.50)","guid":"RVlFHbyxSxmBznWzErtTTA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"Digoxina → OR 1.59","guid":"g866OFU5Q5qGURMSSqd7lg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Diureticos → OR 1.07 (urgencia miccional + deshidratacion)","guid":"l4MKG0lQTEyFHaEbtB93sA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"Betabloqueadores → NO significativa","guid":"dT-IUmrwSTetcLLAcIFGBg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"Vasodilatadores → mayor riesgo","guid":"KbFZbmrQS-u-NRVUESZL6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"72","text":"Antiepilepticos → OR 1.75 (sedacion, ataxia)","guid":"7BmTL2aTSwC8hcDDpcxuXA","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"72","text":"Insulina → RR 2.76; hipoglicemiantes orales sin mayor riesgo","guid":"HCFzsc2DRJ-LKkIfhshYPA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"72","text":"AINEs → OR 1.21 (1.01-1.44)","guid":"n_R-j6luRDyNMFlzH1Ne3A","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"72","text":"Bloqueadores alfa (tamsulosina) → riesgo aumentado","guid":"F3Nm6rPKQZKASjq01xGnQQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"72","text":"Narcoticos → NO asociacion clara","guid":"yzdfkcVGTp-B7QloddA4Jg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Osteosarcopenia","guid":"jb-0NwLkT0yZDG9Pxs9u1w","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Comunicacion bioquimica y mecanica musculo-hueso","guid":"tCA0VpcCT46BdgXEgEWQQA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Sarcopenicos → caen MAS que osteoporoticos","guid":"oYW978SdSpmrHUOm8uOZAg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Osteoporoticos → se fracturan mas pero caen menos","guid":"2YjGWKLKQpOiUwCxeqV_sA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"OSTEOSARCOPENICOS → PEORES outcomes (caen + se fracturan)","guid":"mvtjS-poQ8O-d2i5NWGbXg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"Inhibidores miostatina → en investigacion","guid":"Wd04xgzCR8yWL8MQFlHlwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"Consecuencias","guid":"rOaYvK-ZRwqdwHB8m6-hbQ","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Mayor contribuyente a heridas, discapacidad y muerte prematura","guid":"uf4OcpuOSVaUBNw2CRdCLQ","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Lesiones","guid":"N2Cfn_G9QBaF_E3pRHbfKA","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"27-56% heridas menores","guid":"Z8yR_hcyTRu50BLaF2cgkA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"10-15% heridas mayores","guid":"l3ttEEWZSeKAgcI-jeoUvg","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"14% consultan urgencia","guid":"b11Ul2JIR_6Lsb-m95fONA","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"96","text":"Fractura de cadera","guid":"RPkK2luvRaWBx_uWX8pfBQ","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"95% producto de caidas","guid":"tLE5Qw8OTceyShauP6f4wg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"10-20% se institucionalizan","guid":"r5XapdlkT5CMkV7py5rF9w","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"20-30% fallecen en 12 meses","guid":"G7FIvs7zRc2mzCDgoVGZeQ","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"25-75% NO recuperan estado funcional previo","guid":"JYgrwFG1QW6h0FwQAnbpKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"96","text":"Mortalidad 3x mayor que en jovenes","guid":"o8R2qlLmRySMGAOjk1wIBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"Sindromes Especificos","guid":"ru-TBosaRHa8i4_M8iRC5Q","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Miedo a caer (Sindrome Post-Caida)","guid":"ppN3f6j_RReqR9wkyaH-MQ","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"20-40% de los que caen lo desarrollan","guid":"v-TbfA3NQNa7dI6HbKk9Rw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"50% post fractura de cadera","guid":"xaNOdelkSmK1n_0RXKHp9w","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Predictores → obesidad, dismovilidad","guid":"_HqX8wOKQJ-OszNGiYApMA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"Espiral → debilida