s periodicos","guid":"U27F0PuxSX-TMthnI5scfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"121","text":"Criterios para evaluacion INTEGRAL (si caida en ultimo ano)","guid":"8QdkZ5eZSje3F2QtrVuxxA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":">=2 caidas en 12 meses","guid":"OGEC1aEKSiadof6WCoGOPw","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"Viviendo con fragilidad","guid":"5X4wfhI0QeeluVYS54FooA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"Perdida de conciencia asociada","guid":"TAh65v--QXiLZ-ld-Ow5Xw","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"Lesion que requirio tratamiento","guid":"gSohAd4YQQWZ9Aytn8TK0Q","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"Incapacidad de levantarse solo","guid":"JpYgOu7eRIChbWH5W5xFrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"121","text":"Si 1 caida SIN criterios anteriores → evaluar marcha y balance","guid":"AxFtPgZsSIedrswtEZ9c1g","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Alteracion → programa ejercicio + evaluacion hogar","guid":"V714L_pxTaWbBlcLWdWSUA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"Normal → informacion y consejo actividad fisica","guid":"L8Jw9eZRQQmxGlIi2QCfYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"121","text":"Hospitalizados y residencias → evaluacion integral AUTOMATICA","guid":"SBTTH61WRDy40NovtFYWpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Evaluacion Integral de Caidas","guid":"V6MesVcKSh-S8bIUrjg_CA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Componentes NICE NG249","guid":"lpac-aVFRaSYfufeS4vaNA","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Abuso de alcohol","guid":"P6w9KBAFQi-aDqh0AAQZag","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Examen cardiovascular → PA acostado y de pie (OBLIGATORIO)","guid":"6JjexqAERISrAbCzCvUysg","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"Cognicion y animo","guid":"rPpZPehgSY2CTQQTixtC_g","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"Delirium (hospital/residencia)","guid":"voQNGzjrTKGBZeuUkLCLvQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"Dieta, ingesta liquidos, perdida peso","guid":"Bbqf4ZgbTFW8lTgLxwWFAQ","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"140","text":"Mareo → si vertigo rotatorio → considerar Dix-Hallpike","guid":"Msjic-l9T7ylUTUcWNw-eQ","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"140","text":"Calzado y condicion de pies","guid":"lTYrYaD5Q9ud7bIZMMm8FA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"140","text":"Capacidad funcional percibida + preocupaciones sobre caidas","guid":"6ywVKHSmSQqDQaM_V_67jA","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"140","text":"Marcha, balance, movilidad y fuerza muscular","guid":"n3FeZA1kSByC_vrxrgdXXQ","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"140","text":"Hipoacusia","guid":"R5ITjvodQd65qMRoztyYIw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"140","text":"Condiciones cronicas (artritis, demencia, DM, Parkinson)","guid":"h6VIQzGDQvC8RqpSAOiW3A","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"140","text":"Revision farmacologica","guid":"qgTcDWioSRWzrBMqy9U6jA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"140","text":"Examen neurologico","guid":"dqKYQ5HVQEe1JUqXyEWCEg","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"140","text":"Riesgo osteoporosis","guid":"8hT2M50kRsq_6NyScppXBg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"140","text":"Continencia urinaria","guid":"N5qjIhU3RdG7D3lBcdvTBw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"140","text":"Deficit visual","guid":"92w8Iz2XTwyJdhIMe7rmuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"139","text":"Tests funcionales","guid":"78fW8QwqTSy2pBENwlo5xA","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"TUG → >12s riesgo (CDC); >10s (algunas guias); >30s riesgo mortalidad","guid":"igjWb2wVQ9aJvy_jjbs0MQ","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Estancia unipodal → <5s patologico","guid":"Zok5OecITc-rgnqGalYKhw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Sit to Stand 5x → >12-15s alterado","guid":"7xx6McoDQsmQ_T5ZBZ4sUA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"SPPB → <10 puntos fragilidad y alto riesgo","guid":"Ms4JVQW9TuaE28AZZwhHqw","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"Tinetti → <18 alto riesgo; 19-23 moderado; >=24 bajo","guid":"0rZRKbdkQXSU2IRanYfT3g","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"Test Balance 4 Estaciones → tandem <10s o 1 pie <5s → riesgo","guid":"YYAzgscJQz-JQwvcEJnC7w","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"157","text":"Alcance funcional → <15cm alto riesgo","guid":"e_I7QD2HRv6lhyIKCGjskQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"139","text":"Dual Task → caminar + tarea cognitiva → detecta trastornos subclinicos","guid":"VNb4Ew1uTriWOMfDD3-XEQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"139","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"AI4AP0VxQr-zgXv8Uu4ODg","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Hemograma, ELP, BUN/Crea, glicemia","guid":"oevpV3ciR1yjWYFxGsubYw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"TSH, Vitamina B12, Vitamina D","guid":"wYSmbxlCQ8qIG8jmG8-2GA","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"139","text":"Posturografia y analisis de marcha","guid":"VID2dlB3Skqldrg9HCNXiA","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Variabilidad de marcha → lo que MAS se asocia a caidas","guid":"9iLkINnAQaKMYxrwpQfgQA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"Gait Plasticity → potencial biomarcador de fragilidad","guid":"LDgq0ZiaQ7KAe8qqH4_wAw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Intervenciones","guid":"TuqIF5kTTC2Fl3q9U9YlBA","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Manejo Integral Comunitario (NICE NG249)","guid":"ruEkyT3cSBy_QteLtcc1Jg","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Abordar FR identificados en evaluacion integral","guid":"dipG3fe5QOCifFx27zdsMw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Revision farmacologica estructurada → reducir/suspender farmacos de riesgo","guid":"LdNfQmcKRLuMoMlXRbWFfg","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Vitamina D → suplementar si deficit documentado","guid":"cTKGU41kQ9aF8NSudWqOCA","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"Ejercicio → PIEDRA ANGULAR","guid":"QIKb2whoQVSBgwL1ruS4_Q","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"Evaluacion/intervencion riesgos en hogar","guid":"TbDu_8EjT2SrwSR7swJOHw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"Considerar intervencion quirurgica si aplica (cataratas, podologia)","guid":"WKrstyqJTjKdHwon_oHLPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"172","text":"Ejercicio (Recomendacion A)","guid":"PzA0tei_Ti2eBmCeuHptzA","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Reduce caidas 23% (RR 0.78 Cochrane)","guid":"8Ssnnb9nQGynblSvSjTdyw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"BALANCE Y EQUILIBRIO → fundamental → tandem, Tai Chi, transferencias peso","guid":"iTT0P1RZTQmV5ui1QA8vyA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"Fuerza → vital en fragiles y sarcopenicos","guid":"4BoZ9qe9RneiITRwOsrszw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"Aerobico solo NO basta → debe asociarse a equilibrio","guid":"RzQfoWCURuOYvfhl5z35uw","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"Dosis efectiva → minimo 2h/sem x 25 semanas; intensidad progresiva","guid":"Cue1D9A-SrSKfPUgkMgkcQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"Tai Chi → RR 0.71 en comunidad; ROI 509%","guid":"1SEnv_iiQ4e_4IET2JP1HQ","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"180","text":"Si alteracion marcha/balance SIN otros FR → ofrecer programa ejercicio","guid":"lbF-4b1WTqq9p3HjMUT5Fg","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"172","text":"Programas con evidencia","guid":"aevdDGNZS6eIJvAXQvJAig","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Otago Exercise Program → -35% caidas; ROI 127% (AM >80a fragiles)","guid":"4MkyQMBsSam1-qBxJJFCfw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Tai Chi Moving for Better Balance → -55% caidas; ROI 509%","guid":"18-e9f9iQDGc2hMcBJX1gQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"Stepping On → -30% caidas; ROI 64% (7 semanas)","guid":"G4CliVmeTjOQFCx8DVr7ZA","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"Marcha rapida → -52% caidas","guid":"yIyejGpZQJ223-kPDuJ-gA","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"172","text":"Intervencion ambiental","guid":"pkboBchdSTqMnCdbPeLOtw","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"TO domiciliaria → reduce riesgo 21% (hasta 39% en alto riesgo)","guid":"IHW-9oEoT5OXbOPj5P3IHA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Discapacitados visuales → 41% reduccion","guid":"OSjQo5i_RxyBAJDPmgs7NA","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"Visita aislada enfermeria → NO mostro reduccion","guid":"AJvq4m9USKa8qsPjTMFfAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"172","text":"Oftalmologia","guid":"p8_Hewn6QbaJPCjYo92DWQ","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Cirugia cataratas 1er ojo → -34% caidas","guid":"mSDxnfX6QwGDyymXWw2kWg","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Lentes multifocales/bifocales → AUMENTAN riesgo (suelo borroso)","guid":"XCXKa3DhTUeGhgfw2Zlcmw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"Monofocales pueden reducir caidas 40%","guid":"15F_hhvISCyHTHUyw--e2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"172","text":"Podologia","guid":"Fo2psD1nR-aD1vHH0l3zpg","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Puede disminuir caidas 23%","guid":"k_JsOS1DQ4uIIF1KUfHcSw","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"Plantillas rigidas con textura para input sensitivo","guid":"g58r1x8yT7ai8nnBK79gnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"172","text":"Ayudas tecnicas","guid":"hBHakto1Rg2UpMSeb9KXJA","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"Bastones/andadores → beneficio movilidad pero SIN claro beneficio prevencion","guid":"69bNjnnaQi6NEUH2rVp5AA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"Protectores cadera → RR 0.82 institucionalizados → baja adherencia","guid":"2WUuk9B3REWpIaG8EE7Uwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"172","text":"Residencias y hospitales","guid":"Y9X0uxxMQT-r1zK4j2l19w","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"Evaluacion integral automatica al ingreso","guid":"fU347LGtTzy4YSzvzETnWA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"Abordar FR identificados","guid":"PyYOQLAlRJWQ7Fh9RScuOw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"Revision farmacologica","guid":"_gbErSp_SWSyiFDTNq1j9Q","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"Vitamina D si deficit","guid":"oyTpTeXOSeabb62xgiWNZg","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"207","text":"Ejercicio adaptado","guid":"-EpDJyS8SU6Xa3Un-I_8Cg","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"207","text":"Intervencion ambiental","guid":"UJWGe42oRTuTJMp4Q7kZtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"172","text":"Algoritmo STEADI (CDC)","guid":"gW7LeNpZTjK3iEO2UhyFSQ","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Screen → Stay Independent >=4, caida con lesion, >=2 caidas","guid":"Cn0Q9_vkRaSJGoG0xBji8g","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"Assess → TUG, 30s Chair Stand, 4-Stage Balance, HO","guid":"sWcd4jkwTE6Dz7xHcJ_yaQ","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"Intervene → Vit D, revision meds, Kine/TO, comorbilidades","guid":"2KROz3XASsezU0izXX2Bhw","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"Follow-up → 30-90 dias","guid":"QL5My_9xTZenjw5fpuDWMg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"0","text":"Maximizar Adherencia (NICE NG249)","guid":"YDMqDfz5SCOFDGAlksufRQ","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"Adaptar intervencion a preferencias y capacidades","guid":"XVzj6SnAQOeRNKk5XBnZ4Q","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Considerar barreras (transporte, motivacion, dolor)","guid":"XwwCOdDJSZqakE09ZPmpgQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"NICE → TCC si miedo a caer no mejora con ejercicio","guid":"as28M5IGRWG8nInfE0_Mow","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"Educacion → informar sobre riesgo, beneficios de ejercicio, modificaciones hogar","guid":"A1L-Hxq4SDybVwnDjMFHDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"AEELrQisRF6eW-aFoUgodw","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Caida en ultimo ano = automaticamente en riesgo → predictor mas simple y potente","guid":"PAQgFi0CSTG_pOPmJMEjJg","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"Caida en casa = fragil/enfermo vs caida en calle = activo/vigoroso","guid":"6hh64D6GQuWBsOPhcZgBkQ","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"Mayor riesgo farmacologico → primeras 24h de inicio/ajuste","guid":"NALcc9tASjqkcxwnGiwgDQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"224","text":"Lentes multifocales distorsionan suelo → cambiar a monofocales (-40% caidas)","guid":"pKfOjPXESKe2P6UGA965Ag","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"224","text":"ANTICOAGULACION → riesgo ACV sin ACO supera 10x el riesgo sangrado por caida → NO contraindicar ACO solo por riesgo caidas","guid":"xmManfKLSxeNfA9yI_pfpw","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"224","text":"Mareo postural sin baja PA en cifras → manejar como ortostatismo","guid":"nryO95EfTBa7Gf-HMWcJTA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"224","text":"Dolor → a mayor intensidad y sitios con dolor, mayor riesgo caida","guid":"gXGjVzoJR3S4UvpjQvNhXw","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"224","text":"Post-alta hospitalaria → riesgo paradojico aumentado (hasta 43%) por recuperacion movilidad sin fuerza/balance","guid":"RR22kcm1TNqt-DsiUE77dw","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"224","text":"Deterioro cognitivo no amnesico (frontal) → mas caidas que Alzheimer tipico","guid":"SX75JLFWSaGp4GVtUHQzVg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"224","text":"NICE 2025 amplia cobertura a 50-64a con FR (demencia, Parkinson, discapacidad intelectual)","guid":"_88nFQQgQGaZJwCuuDAwCg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"224","text":"NO usar herramientas predictivas de riesgo → NICE 2025 explicito","guid":"U_ZpdXWuTiS1g1VvDPfAXg","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"224","text":"Variabilidad de marcha → mejor predictor que velocidad aislada","guid":"-QtV_lJ-QrGkOlC7snGjiQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"224","text":"TUG >10-12s → punto de corte clave para iniciar intervencion","guid":"WN9Nd-ThQWyhoUCP5PsLzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","pa